│ (`llvm/lib/Transforms/IPO/SCCP.cpp`). Specifically, the logic that determines whether a    │
│ block can be safely deleted does not account for the presence of predecessors. Before      │
│ deleting a block, the pass must ensure that all incoming edges to the block are removed,   │
│ and the CFG is updated accordingly.\n\n### 4. Proposed Edit Points(s)\nThe edit point is   │
